.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-UPTIME" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-uptime \- show node identity and status summary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-uptime
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns alias, color, peer count, and active channel count from
.BR getinfo .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"alias":..., "color":..., "num_peers":N, "num_active_channels":N, "version":..., "network":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-info (1),
.BR lightning-node-channel-count (1)
